Parliament, Tuesday, 10 September 2019 – The Standing Committee on Appropriations, the Select Committee on Appropriations, and the Portfolio Committee on Public Enterprises will have a joint meeting. The committees will be briefed by the Department of Public Enterprises and Eskom on the Special Appropriation Bill. Details of the meeting: Date : Tuesday, 10 September 2019
	Time : 10:00 – 13:00
	Venue : Committee Room S12A, Ground Floor, NCOP Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the Committee’s Media Officer: Name: Ms Yoliswa Landu
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 8203 
	Cell: 081 497 4694
